description: 777 East Broadway offers the perfect blend of historic charm & modern luxury, boasting soaring ceilings, original details, and a host of recent upgrades. Spanning over 3,600 sf and offering 3-4 bedrooms plus an office and playroom, there's no shortage of room for family and guests. The kitchen is equipped with SS appliances, ample counter space and flows directly onto the back deck which overlooks a large backyard! The newly renovated primary suite encompasses the entire top floor, offering a private retreat complete with a wet bar and a stunning primary bath that boasts a separate soaking tub, radiant floors, and a dual vanity. Downstairs was gutted and is being transformed into a versatile space, with a playroom and a separate area for a gym. Off street parking available via the newly approved permit for a driveway with space for two cars. Ideally located on the East Side near M Street Park, this home offers the best of city living with convenient access to parks, shops, restaurants
